sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Customer
  participant SITE as Website
  participant VIEW as Loyalty View (Web or PWA)
  participant API as Loyalty App API
  participant DB as App Database
  participant OTP as Email OTP Service
  participant R as ROLLER
  participant P as PATCH
  participant EXT as External Events (CRUD)

  U->>SITE: Open website
  SITE->>VIEW: Open loyalty page
  U->>VIEW: Log in with email OTP
  VIEW->>API: POST /auth/otp/request
  API->>OTP: Send one-time code
  VIEW->>API: POST /auth/otp/verify
  VIEW->>API: GET /account
  API-->>VIEW: Return loyalty status and reward status
  VIEW-->>U: Show loyalty progress

  U->>R: Buy park ticket
  opt External create source
    EXT->>R: Create booking event
  end
  R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Created)
  R->>P: Update loyalty field (purchase)
  P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
  U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
  VIEW->>API: GET /account
  API-->>VIEW: Return updated loyalty status

  R-->>U: Booking confirmed
  U->>R: Visit park
  R-->>U: Entry confirmed

  alt Booking includes child tickets linked to a parent account
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Updated with child links)
    R->>P: Update parent loyalty field
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (parent loyalty incremented)
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return parent loyalty update
  end

  alt Booking is edited
    EXT->>R: Update booking event
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Updated)
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (edit)
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (loyalty adjusted)
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return updated booking and loyalty status
  end

  alt External booking is deleted
    EXT->>R: Delete booking event
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Cancelled)
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (delete)
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (loyalty recalculated)
    R-->>U: Booking status updated
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return updated booking and loyalty status
  end

  alt Loyalty target reached
    P->>R: Create one-time free-pass code
    alt PATCH automation webhook delivery
      P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/reward-code
      API->>DB: Save free-pass code as available
    else PATCH custom-field delivery
      U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
      VIEW->>API: GET /account
      API->>P: GET /v2/contacts?email={customerEmail}
      API->>DB: Save free-pass code from PATCH custom field
    end
    VIEW-->>U: Show free-pass code
    U->>R: Use free-pass code in checkout
    R-->>U: Free-pass booking confirmed
    U->>R: Use free pass at entry
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/redemption (Created)
    alt Reset policy
      R->>P: Update loyalty field (counter = 0)
      P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
    else Rolling policy
      R->>P: Update loyalty field (counter reduced)
      P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
    end
    R-->>U: Entry confirmed
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return reward used status and loyalty counter
  end
